|   {{bold}}--- Demonstrating the Aspectran console application with Jetty ---{{bold:off}}
|
|{{underline}}Built-in commands for this console application:{{underline:off}}
|   {{green}}desc on{{fg:off}} - Prints a description of the command each time the command is executed
|   {{green}}desc off{{fg:off}} - Turns off print a description of the command each time the command is executed
|   {{green}}help{{fg:off}} - Prints help for the available commands that was displayed at startup
|   {{green}}restart{{fg:off}} - Restarts this console application
|   {{green}}mem{{fg:off}} - Shows memory usage
|   {{green}}gc{{fg:off}} - Performs a garbage collection
|   {{green}}quit{{fg:off}} - Exits from this console application
|
|{{underline}}Commands that can run examples:{{underline:off}}
|   {{green}}/hello{{fg:off}} - Prints "Hello, World" in the terminal window.
|
